Title: GenoCeptR
Version: 3.0.0
Authors@R: person("Dinuka", "Adasooriya", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dinuka90@yuhs.ac")
Description: Interactive Shiny application for gene expression overlap analysis
    (Venn, Euler, UpSet, Edwards diagrams), overlap/gene list summaries, and
    gprofiler2-based pathway enrichment analysis.
